Currently, this place can only be reached by using

I am the Demon King, Leviathan. I was called the

Is it true... that one of the only seven Demon

(Although I can't sense her presence like Amelia,
I can tell she's not just an ordinary demon.)

How did you come to the surface? There's no way
the Demon King could be summoned without anyone
noticing.

The detection devices of the Greatland Kingdom
should be covering the entire island.

I don't know about that. Were there even detection
devices 300 years ago?

300 years ago! But if that's the case, why didn't
you attack?

There are no records of anyone fighting the
Jealousy King Leviathan in any country.

I have no interest in fighting against humanity. I
only came here because I am interested in the
surface.

I have been living in peace, hiding my true
identity.

...But your subordinates paid a great sacrifice to
summon you, didn't they?
Ah, but what does that matter?

(She really is a demon... Don't be deceived by
appearances.)
So, why are you in the basement of the academy?

I came to this academy for some reason several
decades ago, but I got caught.

Well, because I haven't been in battle for
hundreds of years, I completely let my guard down.

Because I have been using disguise magic all this
time, I have never been exposed as a demon.
No, it's nothing. So, what happened?

Since then, I have been imprisoned in this magic
prison.

It's a pretty powerful barrier, so I can't get out
on my own.

There is something called a teleportation stone,
but I myself cannot use it in any way.
But you can use magic, right?

It seems that the power of the barrier magic has
weakened in recent years.

Well, then you should escape using that. No,
actually, you shouldn't.

...I can only use a part of it. There is no way to
escape from here.

So, I was using a very small amount of magic to
search for allies.
So, that means I reacted to it.
You heard my voice, didn't you?

(And... committed the sin of making a contract
with a demon)

(If I'm found out, I'll definitely be sentenced to
imprisonment... Probably, I won't be able to get
out of prison for the rest of my life)

(This is the worst... to think that I would commit
such a betrayal against Amelia...)
(Do I have to turn myself in...)
Are you listening to my story?
...Did we really go back to the past?
Strictly speaking, it's different, but yes.

This is the magic that can only be used by me to
turn back time in the world.

I can cut out a period of 7 days and repeat it
over and over again.

Only the contractee and I will retain our
memories.
I can't believe such magic exists...

I've never heard of... being able to turn back
time.
But you have returned to the present, haven't you?

You should know. The place where your beloved
girlfriend suffers.

(Certainly... I have no choice but to admit it.
These memories don't seem fake.)

Ah, even if things go well, we just need to dispel
the magic.

And with that, you will be able to obtain the
future you desire.
To think there's such a convenient magic...

But, it's not like you're doing it out of
goodwill, right?

I already mentioned it when we made the contract.
Were you not conscious anymore?
My wish is to escape from this magic barrier.

I want you to find and defeat the person
controlling the magic barrier.

Being trapped is a story from decades ago. Where
are they?

I'm certain. I've had a feeling since last year
that someone has been tampering with the barrier
magic.

It's something that happens occasionally, but
perhaps they are adjusting the barrier.
So find that person who is in the academy.

Of course, there is no right to refuse. We have
already made a contract.

Until I find them, even if you reach the future

(By doing that, I can save Amelia and complete the
mission)

(It's unthinkable to cooperate with a demon, but

(Is it someone else who is imprisoning the one who
caused the incident in the previous timeline and
Leviathan?)

(To imprison the king and perform a large-scale
